13 worst men’s college basketball coaching hires of this century</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://bellottibasketball.substack.com/p/the-nbas-eighth-era-is-upon-us\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The NBA’s Eighth Era Is Upon Us</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏒 <strong><a href=\"https://adamgretz.substack.com/p/connor-mcdavid-and-the-edmonton-oilers?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1019569&amp;post_id=196109118&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Connor McDavid and the Edmonton Oilers are running out of chances with each other</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\"https://adamgretz.substack.com/p/better-luck-next-year-what-is-the?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1019569&amp;post_id=195640058&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Better luck next year: What is the problem with the Columbus Blue Jackets?</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏒<strong> <a href=\"https://bfarrell27.substack.com/p/the-kings-went-out-with-a-whimper\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Kings went out with a whimper</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏒 <strong><a href=\"https://www.houseofstrauss.com/p/the-nhls-ratings-surge-has-an-awkward?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=446127&amp;post_id=191653187&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The NHL’s Ratings Surge Has an Awkward Explanation</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://almostcooperstown.substack.com/p/cody-and-corey-used-to-be-dodgers?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1216321&amp;post_id=195869991&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=f